152
01:03:42,370 --> 01:04:08,020
identifying for wards eight and four and just confirming that we have the right spots for it. A little bit of a strategy in terms of the advertising plan for it and leaving it open enough for enough time for anyone to reach out. Love the idea of any super volunteers. So certainly in each of these different wards, if you would be willing to help, you know, please again reach out to me and we can start kind of putting that in there as well.

153
01:04:08,020 --> 01:04:35,408
